   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>THE LORD'S TABLE MEETING 6 Scripture Reading: Lev 3:1-17; 7:23, 25-27, 33 OUTLINE Presenting Christ as the peace offering to the Father: The enjoyment of the peace offering: God's portion: The blood 3:2, 8, 13, 17; 7:26-27, 33: 1 To satisfy His righteous requirements.</S>
