   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Rom 3:23.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>The fat 3:3-4, 9-10, 14-17; 7:23, 25, 33: 1 The inward riches for His satisfaction according to His glory.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>2 The protection of the inwards.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>The two kidneys the most tender part of the inwards 3:4, 10, 15.</S>
